The paper presents a robotic system that utilizes vision-based techniques for automatic package dispatching. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics and Control). The paper also involves the use of deep learning techniques for package recognition, which falls under the category of cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper proposes improvements to a sampling algorithm, which could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves the design of a multi-modal robot hand, which could be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia).
